1
00:00:55,667 --> 00:00:59,333
<i>Harap perhatikan pengumuman penting ini.</i>

2
00:01:37,458 --> 00:01:40,583
<i>Jutaan orang telah terkena dampak kejahatan.</i>

3
00:01:43,375 --> 00:01:46,333
<i>Keresahan masyarakat memuncak.</i>

4
00:01:46,458 --> 00:01:48,583
<i>Pengangguran dan tunawisma yang merajalela</i>

5
00:01:48,708 --> 00:01:50,792
<i>membuat Los Angeles penuh kejahatan.</i>

6
00:01:50,917 --> 00:01:51,958
PERUSUH DAN POLISI BENTROK

7
00:01:52,083 --> 00:01:53,125
<i>Penjara penuh.</i>

8
00:01:53,250 --> 00:01:54,208
PENJARA LA PENUH 3 TAHUN BERUNTUN

9
00:01:55,208 --> 00:01:57,125
{\an8}<i>Zona Merah kota ditetapkan</i>

10
00:01:57,250 --> 00:02:00,833
{\an8}<i>untuk membatasi individu yang terlibat kekerasan.</i>

11
00:02:02,000 --> 00:02:03,208
KERUSUHAN HOLLYWOOD

12
00:02:03,333 --> 00:02:05,667
<i>Tetap saja, ratusan pahlawan berseragam biru</i>

13
00:02:05,792 --> 00:02:07,333
{\an8}<i>tewas saat bertugas.</i>

14
00:02:07,458 --> 00:02:10,250
{\an8}<i>Situasi ekstrem butuh solusi ekstrem.</i>

15
00:02:10,375 --> 00:02:12,333
Kita butuh Sidang Mercy

16
00:02:12,458 --> 00:02:15,375
dan aku akan meyakinkan kolegaku di kedua kubu

17
00:02:15,500 --> 00:02:16,542
untuk mendukungnya.

18
00:02:16,667 --> 00:02:17,792
DEPARTEMEN KEHAKIMAN LA
KEADILAN BAGI SEMUA

19
00:02:17,917 --> 00:02:19,792
<i>Setelah dua tahun beroperasi,</i>

20
00:02:19,917 --> 00:02:23,250
<i>program ini membuat kita bisa tidur nyenyak.</i>

21
00:02:24,167 --> 00:02:28,167
<i>Pelaku kejahatan berat
kini dihakimi oleh akal imitasi</i>

22
00:02:28,292 --> 00:02:30,375
<i>yang mengurangi sidang panjang</i>

23
00:02:30,500 --> 00:02:32,458
<i>dengan bertindak sebagai hakim,</i>

24
00:02:32,583 --> 00:02:33,625
<i>juri,</i>

25
00:02:33,750 --> 00:02:35,042
{\an8}<i>sekaligus algojo.</i>

26
00:02:35,167 --> 00:02:37,083
<i>Di ruang sidang yang otomatis ini,</i>

27
00:02:37,208 --> 00:02:39,625
<i>tersangka dianggap bersalah</i>

28
00:02:39,750 --> 00:02:41,500
<i>sampai terbukti tak bersalah.</i>

29
00:02:42,750 --> 00:02:45,792
<i>Mercy menganalisis semuanya dengan sangat akurat,</i>

30
00:02:45,917 --> 00:02:48,042
<i>menjangkau data yang sangat luas,</i>

31
00:02:48,167 --> 00:02:51,042
<i>termasuk bukti dari LAPD</i>

32
00:02:51,167 --> 00:02:52,750
<i>dan tim quadcopter-nya.</i>

33
00:02:52,875 --> 00:02:54,458
<i>Sejak peluncuran program ini,</i>

34
00:02:54,583 --> 00:02:57,125
{\an8}<i>secara imparsial, Mercy sudah menghakimi,</i>

35
00:02:57,250 --> 00:03:00,417
{\an8}<i>mendakwa, dan mengeksekusi 18 individu,</i>

36
00:03:01,917 --> 00:03:04,708
<i>mengurangi kejahatan di kota sebanyak 68%.</i>

37
00:03:04,833 --> 00:03:06,667
<i>Menghemat jutaan dolar uang pajak</i>

38
00:03:06,792 --> 00:03:10,125
<i>berkat akurasi dan efisiensi programnya.</i>

39
00:03:10,250 --> 00:03:12,833
<i>Mercy menggunakan fakta dan banyak bukti</i>

40
00:03:12,958 --> 00:03:15,458
<i>untuk menjamin keadilan ditegakkan</i>

41
00:03:15,583 --> 00:03:18,417
<i>dalam beberapa jam setelah pembunuhan terjadi.</i>

42
00:03:18,542 --> 00:03:20,458
<i>Ini pencegah kejahatan mutakhir.</i>

43
00:03:20,583 --> 00:03:23,000
<i>Kebebasan yang dicintai semua warga Amerika</i>

44
00:03:23,125 --> 00:03:26,375
<i>kini dilindungi oleh sistem
yang didesain untuk mengeliminasi ancaman</i>

45
00:03:26,500 --> 00:03:28,333
<i>dengan cepat dan efisien.</i>

46
00:03:28,458 --> 00:03:31,458
<i>Masa depan penegakan hukum adalah Mercy</i>

47
00:03:32,125 --> 00:03:34,542
<i>dan kau kasusnya berikutnya.</i>

48
00:03:35,792 --> 00:03:37,292
<i>Demi menjamin sidang yang adil,</i>

49
00:03:37,417 --> 00:03:40,750
<i>kau, terdakwa, bisa mengakses bukti TKP</i>

50
00:03:40,875 --> 00:03:42,958
<i>dan jejak digital lengkapmu.</i>

51
00:03:43,083 --> 00:03:44,208
Sialan.

52
00:03:44,333 --> 00:03:45,958
- Hei.
<i>- Kau bisa membela diri…</i>

53
00:03:46,083 --> 00:03:48,000
- Bagaimana aku bisa di sini?
<i>- …tapi pahami,</i>

54
00:03:48,125 --> 00:03:50,667
<i>Mercy tak membuat kesalahan.</i>

55
00:03:52,042 --> 00:03:54,917
<i>Kotamu berterima kasih
sudah mengikuti program Mercy.</i>

56
00:03:55,042 --> 00:03:59,167
<i>Kontribusimu mengembalikan kedamaian
dan stabilitas masyarakat kita.</i>

57
00:03:59,292 --> 00:04:03,125
<i>- Mercy adalah keadilan untuk masa depan cerah.</i>
- Lepaskan aku.

58
00:04:03,250 --> 00:04:05,917
<i>- Nomor kasusmu adalah 19.</i>
- Halo?

59
00:04:06,042 --> 00:04:09,708
Halo!

60
00:04:13,667 --> 00:04:16,458
<i>Ini Mahkamah Agung Mercy. Aku Hakim Maddox.</i>

61
00:04:16,583 --> 00:04:18,250
<i>Aku hakim sidangmu hari ini.</i>

62
00:04:18,375 --> 00:04:20,875
Tunggu. Tidak. Apa maksudmu?

63
00:04:21,000 --> 00:04:22,417
Tidak ada sidang.

64
00:04:23,042 --> 00:04:24,208
Aku Detektif Raven.

65
00:04:24,333 --> 00:04:26,708
<i>Harap embuskan napas panjang.</i>

66
00:04:26,833 --> 00:04:29,125
Tunggu. Tunggu… Sebentar.

67
00:04:29,250 --> 00:04:30,708
<i>- Identitas dikonfirmasi.</i>
- Baik…

68
00:04:30,833 --> 00:04:32,500
<i>Harap embuskan napas panjang.</i>

69
00:04:32,625 --> 00:04:34,458
Kubawa delapan orang ke kursi ini.

70
00:04:34,583 --> 00:04:37,250
Aku Chris Raven, Kejahatan Berat.
Ini bukan tempatku.

71
00:04:37,375 --> 00:04:40,083
<i>Harap embuskan napas, Tn. Raven.</i>

72
00:04:41,875 --> 00:04:42,917
<i>Terima kasih.</i>

73
00:04:43,042 --> 00:04:46,167
<i>Kadar alkohol darahmu
sudah cukup layak untuk sidang.</i>

74
00:04:46,292 --> 00:04:47,625
Berapa lama aku pingsan?

75
00:04:47,750 --> 00:04:50,333
{\an8}<i>- Lima jam 26 menit.</i>
- Astaga.

76
00:04:50,458 --> 00:04:54,042
<i>Sebelum kita melanjutkan,
kau harus bersumpah semua kesaksianmu</i>

77
00:04:54,167 --> 00:04:56,500
<i>jujur sebenar-benarnya.</i>

78
00:04:57,958 --> 00:04:58,958
Tunggu.

79
00:05:00,708 --> 00:05:02,917
Tunggu. Ini tak mungkin nyata.

80
00:05:03,042 --> 00:05:05,208
<i>Aku jamin, ini sangat nyata.</i>

81
00:05:05,333 --> 00:05:08,250
<i>- Kau harus bersumpah.</i>
- Jika kau pikir ini nyata…

82
00:05:08,375 --> 00:05:10,208
kau salah besar.

83
00:05:10,333 --> 00:05:13,083
<i>Jika ada kesalahan, aku akan mengungkapkannya,</i>

84
00:05:13,208 --> 00:05:15,917
<i>tapi kau harus mematuhi aturannya dulu.</i>

85
00:05:16,042 --> 00:05:18,042
Baik. Aku bersumpah.

86
00:05:18,167 --> 00:05:19,375
<i>Bersumpah apa?</i>

87
00:05:20,625 --> 00:05:23,333
Untuk bicara sejujur-jujurnya, puas?

88
00:05:24,208 --> 00:05:26,375
Kau bisa jelaskan aku harus jujur soal apa

89
00:05:26,500 --> 00:05:27,583
karena apa pun ini…

90
00:05:27,708 --> 00:05:29,583
<i>Christopher Raven, kau diadili</i>

91
00:05:29,708 --> 00:05:32,208
<i>atas pembunuhan istrimu.</i>

92
00:05:32,333 --> 00:05:33,500
<i>Nicole Raven.</i>

93
00:05:35,708 --> 00:05:36,708
{\an8}MEMBUKA // FAIL BUKTI RAVEN

94
00:05:43,583 --> 00:05:45,167
<i>- Di mana korbannya?
- Di dapur.</i>

95
00:05:45,292 --> 00:05:46,125
<i>Di sini!</i>

96
00:05:47,583 --> 00:05:49,083
<i>- Butuh tim medis!</i>
- Apa?

97
00:05:49,208 --> 00:05:52,292
<i>- Ada orang lain di sini?
- Tak ada. Cuma aku.</i>

98
00:05:52,417 --> 00:05:54,583
<i>- Ya, kami segera masuk.
- Cuma ada ibuku!</i>

99
00:05:54,708 --> 00:05:56,042
<i>- Kau baik-baik saja?
- Ya…</i>

100
00:05:56,167 --> 00:05:57,708
<i>Paramedis di lokasi.</i>

101
00:05:57,833 --> 00:05:59,417
<i>Aku tak tahu dia kenapa!</i>

102
00:05:59,542 --> 00:06:01,542
<i>Perempuan, luka tusuk, pelaku tak dikenal.</i>

103
00:06:01,667 --> 00:06:02,833
<i>Bu, tak apa-apa.</i>

104
00:06:02,958 --> 00:06:05,208
<i>Cobalah tetap diam. Mengerti?</i>

105
00:06:06,000 --> 00:06:08,583
<i>Ya, aku berusaha. Tolong dia!</i>

106
00:06:08,708 --> 00:06:09,875
<i>Siapa pelakunya?</i>

107
00:06:10,667 --> 00:06:11,792
<i>Tolong ibuku.</i>

108
00:06:11,917 --> 00:06:13,417
<i>Siapa?</i>

109
00:06:13,542 --> 00:06:14,708
<i>Chris.</i>

110
00:06:14,833 --> 00:06:16,292
Itu mustahil.

111
00:06:16,833 --> 00:06:18,458
- Astaga.
<i>- Sidang mempersembahkan</i>

112
00:06:18,583 --> 00:06:22,125
<i>pernyataan pembuka yang membuktikan
hubunganmu dengan korban.</i>

113
00:06:22,250 --> 00:06:24,750
- Astaga! Ya ampun!
<i>- Puncaknya hari ini…</i>

114
00:06:24,875 --> 00:06:27,333
<i>saat cuma ada kau dan Nicole di rumah</i>

115
00:06:27,458 --> 00:06:29,875
<i>ketika penusukan fatalnya terjadi.</i>

116
00:06:30,667 --> 00:06:32,750
- Bohong.
<i>- Silakan periksa sendiri.</i>

117
00:06:32,875 --> 00:06:33,917
MEMBUKA // PERAMBAN

118
00:06:34,042 --> 00:06:37,542
<i>Akses perintah suara
dan kontrol sentuh telah diberikan.</i>

119
00:06:40,625 --> 00:06:41,625
Baik.

120
00:06:44,167 --> 00:06:45,208
<i>Tn. Raven.</i>

121
00:06:45,333 --> 00:06:46,375
KESALAHAN FATAL

122
00:06:46,500 --> 00:06:48,250
<i>Akses perintah suara
dan kontrol sentuh telah diberikan.</i>

123
00:06:48,375 --> 00:06:51,125
Cari… Bisa cari Nicole Raven?

124
00:06:57,667 --> 00:06:59,000
DETEKTIF LAPD DI SIDANG MERCY

125
00:07:04,208 --> 00:07:05,875
<i>Opsir LAPD, Chris Raven,</i>

126
00:07:06,000 --> 00:07:08,750
<i>telah ditangkap hari ini atas pembunuhan istrinya.</i>

127
00:07:08,875 --> 00:07:10,833
{\an8}<i>Raven dan rekannya, Jaq Diallo…</i>

128
00:07:10,958 --> 00:07:13,125
{\an8}<i>adalah pendukung awal program Mercy</i>

129
00:07:13,250 --> 00:07:15,958
{\an8}<i>dan bertanggung jawab atas penangkapan David Webb</i>

130
00:07:16,083 --> 00:07:17,792
{\an8}<i>serta mengadili si pembunuh</i>

131
00:07:17,917 --> 00:07:20,375
{\an8}<i>sebagai peserta pertama Sidang Mercy</i>

132
00:07:20,500 --> 00:07:21,917
{\an8}<i>dua tahun lalu.</i>

133
00:07:22,042 --> 00:07:25,333
{\an8}<i>Aku bangga bisa membawa
tersangka pertama untuk sidang ini</i>

134
00:07:25,458 --> 00:07:27,750
{\an8}<i>dan akan terus membawakan lagi</i>

135
00:07:27,875 --> 00:07:30,917
{\an8}<i>- sampai pesannya tersampaikan.
- Ini luar biasa.</i>

136
00:07:31,042 --> 00:07:33,667
<i>Dulu dia mengirim orang ke Sidang Mercy,</i>

137
00:07:33,792 --> 00:07:35,708
<i>kini dia sendiri di sini.</i>

138
00:07:36,833 --> 00:07:38,250
<i>Tn. Raven, apa pengakuanmu?</i>

139
00:07:40,917 --> 00:07:42,958
<i>Tn. Raven, apa pengakuanmu?</i>

140
00:07:45,083 --> 00:07:46,542
Tidak bersalah.

141
00:07:46,667 --> 00:07:48,500
Aku tidak bersalah.

142
00:07:48,625 --> 00:07:50,542
Tak mungkin aku menyakitinya.

143
00:07:50,667 --> 00:07:51,833
<i>Berdasarkan bukti,</i>

144
00:07:51,958 --> 00:07:54,583
<i>aku sudah menilai kemungkinan kau bersalah</i>

145
00:07:54,708 --> 00:07:56,750
<i>adalah 97,5%.</i>

146
00:07:56,875 --> 00:07:59,042
<i>Ini 17,5% di atas</i>

147
00:07:59,167 --> 00:08:02,583
<i>ambang batas 80% untuk memicu sidang Mercy.</i>

148
00:08:04,375 --> 00:08:05,917
MEMBUKA // AWAN MUNISIPAL

149
00:08:06,667 --> 00:08:09,333
<i>Ini Awan Munisipal Los Angeles.</i>

150
00:08:09,458 --> 00:08:12,750
<i>Setiap warga dan organisasi diwajibkan oleh hukum</i>

151
00:08:12,875 --> 00:08:15,000
<i>untuk menghubungkan perangkat mereka.</i>

152
00:08:17,208 --> 00:08:19,625
<i>Aku punya akses penuh servernya selama sidang.</i>

153
00:08:20,708 --> 00:08:24,625
<i>Ini dasar dari kemampuanku untuk membuat putusan.</i>

154
00:08:26,542 --> 00:08:29,458
<i>Kau boleh gunakan
sumber daya apa pun di sidang ini</i>

155
00:08:29,583 --> 00:08:32,042
<i>untuk membuktikan bahwa kau tak bersalah.</i>

156
00:08:32,167 --> 00:08:33,625
<i>Jika kau dinyatakan bersalah,</i>

157
00:08:33,750 --> 00:08:36,167
<i>kau akan dieksekusi</i>

158
00:08:36,292 --> 00:08:37,750
<i>- dalam 90 menit.</i>
- Tidak.

159
00:08:37,875 --> 00:08:41,250
<i>- Sidangmu dimulai sekarang.</i>
- Tidak.

160
00:08:42,417 --> 00:08:44,583
Ini salah. Semuanya salah!

161
00:08:44,708 --> 00:08:46,625
- Kau harus matikan ini!
<i>- Tidak bisa.</i>

162
00:08:46,750 --> 00:08:48,792
<i>Sistem AI dilarang hukum</i>

163
00:08:48,917 --> 00:08:51,875
<i>untuk terlibat langsung
dalam mencabut nyawa manusia.</i>

164
00:08:52,000 --> 00:08:54,792
<i>Kursinya bersistem tertutup di luar kendaliku,</i>

165
00:08:54,917 --> 00:08:56,958
<i>itu tak akan mengeluarkan denyut sonik fatal</i>

166
00:08:57,083 --> 00:09:00,167
<i>jika sidangnya kuakhiri sebelum waktu habis.</i>

167
00:09:00,292 --> 00:09:02,542
<i>Agar itu terjadi, kemungkinan bersalahmu</i>

168
00:09:02,667 --> 00:09:05,792
<i>harus turun ke bawah ambang batas 92%</i>

169
00:09:05,917 --> 00:09:07,167
<i>keraguan yang masuk akal.</i>

170
00:09:07,292 --> 00:09:09,875
Aku bukan pembunuh, aku di pihakmu.

171
00:09:10,000 --> 00:09:12,500
Aku di pihakmu! Kau ingat David Webb?

172
00:09:12,625 --> 00:09:14,500
Kau ingat David Webb?

173
00:09:14,625 --> 00:09:15,875
Siapa yang memulai ini? Aku!

174
00:09:16,000 --> 00:09:17,917
<i>Aku tahu persis siapa dirimu.</i>

175
00:09:18,042 --> 00:09:20,833
<i>Aku tahu semua perbuatanmu
untuk sidang ini. Terima kasih.</i>

176
00:09:21,458 --> 00:09:23,167
- Baik. Apa?
<i>- Tapi perbuatanmu dulu</i>

177
00:09:23,292 --> 00:09:24,708
<i>tidak lagi signifikan.</i>

178
00:09:24,833 --> 00:09:28,542
<i>Di sini, cuma fakta yang bisa menghukummu</i>

179
00:09:28,667 --> 00:09:31,125
<i>atau mungkin menyelamatkanmu.</i>

180
00:09:31,250 --> 00:09:34,875
MEMULAI // PRESENTASI BUKTI

181
00:09:35,000 --> 00:09:38,625
<i>Kau tiba di kantor pukul 08.51 pagi ini,</i>

182
00:09:38,750 --> 00:09:41,042
<i>tapi tak keluar dari mobilmu.</i>

183
00:09:42,125 --> 00:09:45,417
<i>Kau malah kembali ke rumahmu.</i>

184
00:09:48,125 --> 00:09:49,250
KAMERA, PINTU DEPAN

185
00:09:53,708 --> 00:09:56,625
<i>Kau harus pergi dari sini. Aku sudah muak.</i>

186
00:09:56,750 --> 00:09:57,917
<i>Buka pintunya.</i>

187
00:09:58,708 --> 00:10:00,333
<i>Tak akan kubuka.</i>

188
00:10:00,458 --> 00:10:02,250
<i>Bicaralah lewat pengacara.</i>

189
00:10:02,833 --> 00:10:04,708
<i>Aku punya kuncinya di mobilku.</i>

190
00:10:04,833 --> 00:10:07,792
<i>Aku akan ambil dan membuka pintu ini.
Bisakah kau…</i>

191
00:10:07,917 --> 00:10:09,917
<i>- bersikap dewasa?
- Chris, jangan.</i>

192
00:10:19,667 --> 00:10:22,000
<i>Jangan masuk! Keluar dari rumahku!</i>

193
00:10:22,125 --> 00:10:23,292
<i>Keluar dari rumahku!</i>

194
00:10:24,250 --> 00:10:27,500
<i>Kau menghabiskan 26 menit
di dalam rumah bersama Nicole.</i>

195
00:10:30,542 --> 00:10:32,958
<i>Putrimu kembali dari menginap.</i>

196
00:10:33,083 --> 00:10:34,083
<i>Ibu?</i>

197
00:10:45,333 --> 00:10:48,250
<i>Data TKP memastikan pada sekitar waktu ini,</i>

198
00:10:48,375 --> 00:10:50,917
<i>Nicole ditusuk oleh pria bertangan kanan</i>

199
00:10:51,042 --> 00:10:52,917
<i>dan luka satu tusukannya sangat agresif</i>

200
00:10:53,042 --> 00:10:56,500
{\an8}<i>sampai menggores satu vertebra
sekaligus menembus levernya…</i>

201
00:10:56,625 --> 00:10:59,708
- Tidak.
<i>- dan memutus arteri mesenterikanya.</i>

202
00:10:59,833 --> 00:11:01,917
- Itu bukan aku.
<i>- Kau bertangan kanan.</i>

203
00:11:02,042 --> 00:11:05,458
<i>Noda darah istrimu ditemukan
pada pakaianmu hari ini…</i>

204
00:11:05,583 --> 00:11:06,708
<i>dan nodanya baru.</i>

205
00:11:06,833 --> 00:11:09,583
<i>Dari rumah, kau mengemudi ke Bar Harbor Master</i>

206
00:11:09,708 --> 00:11:11,042
<i>dan minum cukup banyak.</i>

207
00:11:11,167 --> 00:11:12,167
Tidak!

208
00:11:12,792 --> 00:11:13,792
<i>Apa kau haus?</i>

209
00:11:16,083 --> 00:11:18,167
- Ya.
<i>- Kau sakit kepala?</i>

210
00:11:18,292 --> 00:11:20,250
- Ya.
<i>- Dehidrasi dan sakit kepalamu</i>

211
00:11:20,375 --> 00:11:23,917
<i>adalah akibat kadar alkohol darah 0,16
pada waktu penangkapanmu.</i>

212
00:11:24,042 --> 00:11:26,792
Tidak mungkin. Aku tidak pergi ke bar!

213
00:11:26,917 --> 00:11:28,667
- Aku tak ke bar! Mustahil!
<i>- Kau ditangkap</i>

214
00:11:28,792 --> 00:11:30,292
<i>di Bar Harbor Master…</i>

215
00:11:30,417 --> 00:11:32,667
Bohong. Kau berbohong.

216
00:11:32,792 --> 00:11:34,583
<i>Aku tidak berbohong.</i>

217
00:11:34,708 --> 00:11:36,667
<i>Begitu pun faktanya.</i>

218
00:11:36,792 --> 00:11:39,292
MENGAKSES // ARSIP VIDEO //
BAR HARBOR MASTER // 11.40

219
00:11:40,875 --> 00:11:42,542
<i>Ya, Opsir. Itu orangnya.</i>

220
00:11:45,375 --> 00:11:47,458
<i>Hei, Chris. Kau baik-baik saja?</i>

221
00:11:49,708 --> 00:11:51,292
<i>Detektif, kita harus pergi.</i>

222
00:11:51,417 --> 00:11:53,458
<i>Tidak. Aku mau di sini dan minum lagi.</i>

223
00:11:53,583 --> 00:11:55,458
<i>- Kau sudah cukup minum.
- Ayo!</i>

224
00:11:56,708 --> 00:11:57,708
<i>Lepaskan aku!</i>

225
00:12:06,125 --> 00:12:07,375
<i>Hei, apa yang…</i>

226
00:12:17,792 --> 00:12:18,833
<i>Mundur!</i>

227
00:12:18,958 --> 00:12:20,458
<i>Chris, hentikan. Jangan begini.</i>

228
00:12:20,583 --> 00:12:22,125
<i>Baik.</i>

229
00:12:24,958 --> 00:12:25,958
Sial!

230
00:12:26,667 --> 00:12:28,417
<i>Hei! Jangan! Berhenti!</i>

231
00:12:28,542 --> 00:12:30,375
<i>Ayolah, Chris. Sudah cukup.</i>

232
00:12:31,333 --> 00:12:32,333
<i>Hei, tangkap dia!</i>

233
00:12:35,667 --> 00:12:36,875
<i>- Kau, berhenti!
- Hei!</i>

234
00:12:37,000 --> 00:12:39,708
<i>- Keluar.
- Apa yang kau… Pergi! Lepaskan dia!</i>

235
00:12:39,833 --> 00:12:41,583
<i>Astaga! Lepaskan aku!</i>

236
00:12:41,708 --> 00:12:43,375
<i>Hentikan ini, Chris! Berhenti!</i>

237
00:12:43,500 --> 00:12:44,583
<i>Jika kau tidak keluar…</i>

238
00:12:46,417 --> 00:12:47,417
<i>Balikkan.</i>

239
00:12:49,500 --> 00:12:52,958
<i>Mungkin jumlah besar alkohol yang kau konsumsi</i>

240
00:12:53,083 --> 00:12:55,333
<i>dan pukulan ke kepalamu memengaruhi ingatanmu.</i>

241
00:12:55,458 --> 00:12:58,208
Aku tidak ingat… Aku tidak ingat barnya.

242
00:12:58,333 --> 00:13:01,625
<i>Maksudku, kau mungkin tak ingat membunuh istrimu.</i>

243
00:13:02,250 --> 00:13:04,125
<i>- Angkat dia.
- Baringkan. Lapor.</i>

244
00:13:04,250 --> 00:13:06,458
<i>Atau mungkin kau yang berbohong.</i>

245
00:13:07,000 --> 00:13:09,500
<i>Aku mempelajari satu hal di sidang ini, yaitu…</i>

246
00:13:10,333 --> 00:13:12,333
<i>semuanya berbohong.</i>

247
00:13:12,458 --> 00:13:14,167
<i>Kenapa kau kembali ke rumah?</i>

248
00:13:14,292 --> 00:13:15,750
Tidak. Aku tidak…

249
00:13:15,875 --> 00:13:17,500
Aku tidak ingat apa pun! Kenapa…

250
00:13:17,625 --> 00:13:18,750
Aku harus pergi.

251
00:13:18,875 --> 00:13:19,958
<i>Cuma satu caranya,</i>

252
00:13:20,083 --> 00:13:22,750
<i>- jadi, fokus. Kau mau membantah?</i>
- Keluarkan aku!

253
00:13:22,875 --> 00:13:25,167
<i>Tentang mabuk atau tentang putrimu?</i>

254
00:13:25,292 --> 00:13:26,792
Astaga. Britt.

255
00:13:28,333 --> 00:13:30,417
- Biar aku bicara kepadanya.
<i>- Kecuali saksi</i>

256
00:13:30,542 --> 00:13:31,583
<i>kejahatan yang terjadi,</i>

257
00:13:31,708 --> 00:13:32,958
<i>remaja dikecualikan</i>

258
00:13:33,083 --> 00:13:35,250
<i>- dari sidang Mercy.</i>
- Dia putriku.

259
00:13:35,375 --> 00:13:37,625
<i>Namun, kau boleh mengulas kesaksian putrimu</i>

260
00:13:37,750 --> 00:13:39,292
<i>- jika mau.</i>
- Ibunya tewas.

261
00:13:39,417 --> 00:13:41,708
- <i>- Dia bersama orang tua mendiang istrimu.</i>
- Aku

262
00:13:41,833 --> 00:13:43,583
mau bicara

263
00:13:43,708 --> 00:13:45,125
kepada putriku!

264
00:13:48,125 --> 00:13:50,500
Aku mau panggilan pribadiku. Sekarang.

265
00:13:52,292 --> 00:13:54,625
{\an8}<i>Kau boleh mengajukan permintaan menelepon.</i>

266
00:13:56,167 --> 00:13:57,625
<i>Aturan sidang ini mewajibkan,</i>

267
00:13:57,750 --> 00:14:00,208
<i>jika mau menghubungi kenalan mendiang,</i>

268
00:14:00,333 --> 00:14:03,458
<i>harus ada permintaan tertulis
selama masa berkabung.</i>

269
00:14:03,583 --> 00:14:05,333
<i>Jadi, kau boleh mendiktenya.</i>

270
00:14:05,458 --> 00:14:06,500
Baik.

271
00:14:08,625 --> 00:14:10,708
<i>Kau boleh mendikte sekarang, Tn. Raven.</i>

272
00:14:10,833 --> 00:14:12,917
Aku sudah dengar.

273
00:14:17,833 --> 00:14:20,958
Hei, Britt. Ayah harus bicara kepadamu.

274
00:14:23,250 --> 00:14:25,500
Kau akan dengar berita buruk tentang Ayah,

275
00:14:25,625 --> 00:14:27,125
tapi itu tidak benar.

276
00:14:27,250 --> 00:14:28,250
Cuma…

277
00:14:33,833 --> 00:14:35,542
Cuma… Hapus.

278
00:14:36,125 --> 00:14:37,125
Mulai ulang.

279
00:14:43,250 --> 00:14:44,292
Hei, Nak.

280
00:14:45,000 --> 00:14:47,000
Ayah tak menyakiti ibumu.

281
00:14:47,125 --> 00:14:48,167
Ayah tak akan…

282
00:14:48,292 --> 00:14:50,083
Hapus.

283
00:14:50,208 --> 00:14:51,458
TAMBAHKAN PESAN PRIBADI

284
00:14:51,583 --> 00:14:52,917
Sial.

285
00:14:53,500 --> 00:14:56,917
<i>Mungkin aku bisa mengirimkan
permintaan otomatis tanpa pesan pribadi.</i>

286
00:14:57,625 --> 00:14:58,917
Ya. Lakukan.

287
00:14:59,917 --> 00:15:01,625
<i>Permintaan generik dikirim.</i>

288
00:15:04,000 --> 00:15:06,042
<i>Di luar tingkat kejahatanmu,</i>

289
00:15:06,167 --> 00:15:09,042
<i>sidang ini mewajibkan memberimu kesempatan</i>

290
00:15:09,167 --> 00:15:10,667
<i>untuk bicara dengan sponsormu</i>

291
00:15:10,792 --> 00:15:13,583
<i>dan kau akan bicara dengannya
sebelum kita melanjutkan.</i>

292
00:15:13,708 --> 00:15:14,667
ROBERT NELSON
MEMANGGIL

293
00:15:14,792 --> 00:15:15,417
<i>Ya.</i>

294
00:15:17,000 --> 00:15:18,125
- Rob.
<i>- Chris, hei.</i>

295
00:15:18,250 --> 00:15:19,292
Rob, aku tidak ingat.

296
00:15:19,417 --> 00:15:21,208
- Aku tak ingat apa pun.
<i>- Chris, stop.</i>

297
00:15:21,333 --> 00:15:22,167
Aku tak ingat.

298
00:15:22,292 --> 00:15:23,167
<i>Dengar…</i>

299
00:15:23,292 --> 00:15:27,167
<i>mereka mau aku mengikuti AA, jadi…</i>

300
00:15:27,292 --> 00:15:28,375
<i>Kau…</i>

301
00:15:29,333 --> 00:15:31,167
<i>Kau seharusnya meneleponku.</i>

302
00:15:31,292 --> 00:15:33,833
<i>Jika kau berpikir… Jika berpikir soal mabuk.</i>

303
00:15:33,958 --> 00:15:35,417
- Itu tak penting, Rob.
<i>- Telepon aku.</i>

304
00:15:35,542 --> 00:15:37,750
- Itu tak penting.
<i>- Jadi, apa…</i>

305
00:15:37,875 --> 00:15:39,750
- Bung, Nic…
<i>- Chris.</i>

306
00:15:44,125 --> 00:15:46,417
<i>Saat dia tak datang bekerja pagi ini…</i>

307
00:15:46,542 --> 00:15:47,542
<i>Aku…</i>

308
00:15:48,500 --> 00:15:52,083
<i>Aku menghubungi depotnya begitu mendengarnya.</i>

309
00:15:52,208 --> 00:15:53,792
<i>Semua orang di sini…</i>

310
00:15:55,083 --> 00:15:56,750
<i>sangat kacau karena ini.</i>

311
00:15:56,875 --> 00:15:58,333
Aku tak mungkin menyakitinya.

312
00:15:58,458 --> 00:15:59,667
Aku bersumpah.

313
00:15:59,792 --> 00:16:02,417
<i>Chris, aku percaya karma, jadi…</i>

314
00:16:03,000 --> 00:16:04,583
<i>Apa pun yang telah</i>

315
00:16:04,708 --> 00:16:05,708
<i>kau lakukan</i>

316
00:16:06,375 --> 00:16:07,958
<i>atau tak lakukan,</i>

317
00:16:08,083 --> 00:16:10,792
<i>dia akan menjadi sahabatmu hari ini</i>

318
00:16:10,917 --> 00:16:13,500
<i>atau jalang terburuk dalam hidupmu.</i>

319
00:16:13,625 --> 00:16:15,542
<i>Terima kasih, Tn. Nelson, sekian.</i>

320
00:16:15,667 --> 00:16:17,917
- Tunggu. Sebentar. Aku…
<i>- Hei, kau dengar?</i>

321
00:16:18,042 --> 00:16:19,042
Tunggu…

322
00:16:20,542 --> 00:16:21,583
Dia ke mana?

323
00:16:21,708 --> 00:16:24,500
<i>Tn. Nelson cuma dihubungi untuk membahas kambuhmu.</i>

324
00:16:24,625 --> 00:16:26,417
<i>Kau memilih menolak dukungannya.</i>

325
00:16:26,542 --> 00:16:29,375
Dia mengenalku, dia mengenal Nic.

326
00:16:29,500 --> 00:16:31,542
Telepon dia lagi. Kumohon.

327
00:16:31,667 --> 00:16:33,833
Dia akan memberitahumu Nic dan aku bahagia.

328
00:16:33,958 --> 00:16:36,250
<i>Aku sudah mengetahui kondisi pernikahanmu.</i>

329
00:16:37,083 --> 00:16:38,375
Apa maksudmu?

330
00:16:38,500 --> 00:16:39,958
MEMUAT // PROFIL TERDAKWA

331
00:16:40,083 --> 00:16:42,917
<i>Kau memacari Nicole Martin 20 tahun lalu.</i>

332
00:16:43,042 --> 00:16:46,625
<i>Setelah tiga tahun,
kalian menikah di Pantai Redondo.</i>

333
00:16:46,750 --> 00:16:49,083
<i>Chris orang terbaik yang kukenal.</i>

334
00:16:50,875 --> 00:16:52,125
<i>Lalu Nicole muncul</i>

335
00:16:52,250 --> 00:16:54,625
<i>dan entah bagaimana membuat Chris lebih baik.</i>

336
00:16:54,750 --> 00:16:56,417
<i>Untuk Chris dan Nicole!</i>

337
00:16:59,250 --> 00:17:00,375
<i>Siap atau tidak…</i>

338
00:17:03,042 --> 00:17:04,166
<i>Pasti anak lelaki.</i>

339
00:17:05,000 --> 00:17:06,208
<i>Pasti perempuan,</i>

340
00:17:06,333 --> 00:17:08,541
<i>- tapi Ray nama yang kuat.
- Tidak.</i>

341
00:17:08,666 --> 00:17:11,291
<i>Putrimu, Britt Raven, lahir setahun kemudian.</i>

342
00:17:11,416 --> 00:17:15,250
<i>Inilah keluarga baru Raven yang indah.</i>

343
00:17:15,375 --> 00:17:16,666
<i>Aku Paman Ray.</i>

344
00:17:16,791 --> 00:17:18,083
<i>Ini Paman Jimmy.</i>

345
00:17:23,333 --> 00:17:25,250
<i>Kehidupanmu di rumah stabil</i>

346
00:17:26,083 --> 00:17:29,542
<i>sampai kau mengalami
pengalaman traumatis saat bertugas.</i>

347
00:17:30,792 --> 00:17:33,292
<i>Apa yang terjadi?</i>

348
00:17:33,417 --> 00:17:34,458
<i>Ada apa, Sayang?</i>

349
00:17:34,583 --> 00:17:36,500
<i>- Ray tewas.
- Apa? Sayang…</i>

350
00:17:36,625 --> 00:17:39,083
<i>Kematian rekanmu mengubah segalanya</i>

351
00:17:39,208 --> 00:17:41,125
<i>- bagimu dan keluargamu.
- Kau di mana?</i>

352
00:17:41,250 --> 00:17:42,583
<i>Aku mencemaskanmu.</i>

353
00:17:42,708 --> 00:17:44,875
<i>- Ada apa sampai meneleponku?
- Kau pasti mabuk.</i>

354
00:17:45,000 --> 00:17:46,458
<i>Aku mengandalkan jabatan letnan</i>

355
00:17:46,583 --> 00:17:47,708
<i>- untuk itu.
- Britt butuh kamar sendiri.</i>

356
00:17:47,833 --> 00:17:49,583
<i>Kau sudah menjanjikannya.</i>

357
00:17:50,208 --> 00:17:52,125
<i>Itu basemen. Cuma perlu dinding gipsum.</i>

358
00:17:52,250 --> 00:17:54,250
<i>Aku tak mengira akan bercerai.</i>

359
00:17:54,375 --> 00:17:57,542
- Baik. Cukup. Hentikan!
<i>- Ini sangat berat.</i>

360
00:17:57,667 --> 00:18:00,875
- Itu video pribadinya.
<i>- Nicole menjelaskan kau mengamuk</i>

361
00:18:01,000 --> 00:18:02,917
<i>57 kali pada waktu berbeda</i>

362
00:18:03,042 --> 00:18:05,292
<i>dalam pesan dan telepon
dengan keluarga dan temannya…</i>

363
00:18:05,417 --> 00:18:06,458
NIC!
DIA KENAPA?

364
00:18:06,583 --> 00:18:07,708
<i>…selama enam bulan ini.</i>

365
00:18:07,833 --> 00:18:08,875
DIA MENGAMUK LAGI.

366
00:18:09,000 --> 00:18:11,000
{\an8}<i>Namun, ucapan keluargamu
menunjukkan pernikahanmu…</i>

367
00:18:11,125 --> 00:18:12,167
{\an8}AKU TAK MAU BRITT BERSAMANYA BEGINI.

368
00:18:12,292 --> 00:18:13,375
{\an8}<i>…makin renggang karena amarahmu…</i>

369
00:18:13,500 --> 00:18:14,708
DIA JADI BERBEDA SAAT MARAH.

370
00:18:14,833 --> 00:18:16,167
<i>…dan Nicole mempertimbangkan cerai.</i>

371
00:18:16,292 --> 00:18:17,708
AKU MENGHUBUNGI PENGACARA PERCERAIAN.

372
00:18:17,833 --> 00:18:18,875
Aku cinta istriku.

373
00:18:19,000 --> 00:18:21,000
<i>Yang manusia rasakan sebagai cinta</i>

374
00:18:21,125 --> 00:18:23,333
<i>cuma fenomena neurobiologis</i>

375
00:18:23,458 --> 00:18:25,000
<i>yang ditunjukkan dengan pelepasan</i>

376
00:18:25,125 --> 00:18:27,750
<i>dopamin, oksitosin, dan serotonin.</i>

377
00:18:28,625 --> 00:18:30,917
<i>Amarah juga fenomena neurobiologis</i>

378
00:18:31,042 --> 00:18:33,167
<i>dan bisa mengalahkan afeksi.</i>

379
00:18:33,292 --> 00:18:34,333
Maaf. Apa intinya?

380
00:18:34,458 --> 00:18:35,792
<i>Meski pernah mencintai Nicole,</i>

381
00:18:35,917 --> 00:18:37,542
<i>- bukan berarti…
- Mulai lagi!</i>

382
00:18:37,667 --> 00:18:39,292
<i>- …kau tak lepas kendali…
- Biarkan sesukaku.</i>

383
00:18:39,417 --> 00:18:41,125
<i>Tidak, karena kau selalu mengacau.</i>

384
00:18:41,250 --> 00:18:43,792
<i>- Astaga! Chris.
- …dan membunuhnya.</i>

385
00:18:44,750 --> 00:18:46,792
<i>Entah kau ingat atau tidak.</i>

386
00:18:46,917 --> 00:18:49,417
<i>- Nic, kembalilah.
- Ayo, Nak. Ayo pergi.</i>

387
00:18:49,542 --> 00:18:51,000
<i>- Maaf. Ibu tak apa?
- Nic!</i>

388
00:18:51,125 --> 00:18:52,375
<i>Astaga.</i>

389
00:18:54,000 --> 00:18:55,875
Aku bisa agak emosional.

390
00:18:56,000 --> 00:18:57,583
Itu keturunan. Mengerti?

391
00:18:57,708 --> 00:18:59,667
Itu bukan berarti aku membunuh…

392
00:18:59,792 --> 00:19:01,083
<i>Ibu menangis di kamarnya.</i>

393
00:19:01,208 --> 00:19:03,083
<i>Ayah membuat kami takut kemarin.</i>

394
00:19:03,208 --> 00:19:04,500
<i>Sudah kubilang, dia berbahaya.</i>

395
00:19:04,625 --> 00:19:06,542
<i>Aku bisa mengeluarkanmu jika kau mau.</i>

396
00:19:07,500 --> 00:19:09,208
<i>Kau tahu aku bisa mewujudkannya.</i>

397
00:19:09,333 --> 00:19:10,708
<i>Siapa pria ini?</i>

398
00:19:11,750 --> 00:19:14,542
<i>Lagi pula, ibumu tak bisa menghentikanku.</i>

399
00:19:17,208 --> 00:19:18,208
<i>Ya, mungkin.</i>

400
00:19:18,792 --> 00:19:20,625
<i>Aku dengar ibuku bicara soal bercerai.</i>

401
00:19:20,750 --> 00:19:22,583
{\an8}<i>Kuharap dia serius.</i>

402
00:19:25,708 --> 00:19:28,167
<i>Sial. Kau dengar? Ayahku pulang. Aku pergi.</i>

403
00:19:28,292 --> 00:19:29,708
<i>Hei, tunggu.</i>

404
00:19:29,833 --> 00:19:32,625
{\an8}Apa-apaan itu? Kami mengikuti profil Britt.

405
00:19:32,750 --> 00:19:34,042
Dia tak mengunggah ini.

406
00:19:36,625 --> 00:19:38,292
<i>Putrimu punya dua akun aktif.</i>

407
00:19:40,000 --> 00:19:42,458
<i>Sepertinya dia merahasiakan yang ini darimu</i>

408
00:19:42,583 --> 00:19:44,375
{\an8}<i>dengan beberapa profil daring lain…</i>

409
00:19:44,500 --> 00:19:45,542
{\an8}AI BUKAN KEADILAN

410
00:19:45,667 --> 00:19:47,458
{\an8}<i>…tapi semuanya terhubung ke ponselnya.</i>

411
00:19:47,583 --> 00:19:48,625
{\an8}CEGAH AI MENGAMBIL ALIH!

412
00:19:48,750 --> 00:19:49,750
{\an8}Astaga.

413
00:19:50,708 --> 00:19:53,292
{\an8}Ya ampun, dia masih 16 tahun.

414
00:19:54,833 --> 00:19:56,667
Ini bukan Britt.

415
00:19:56,792 --> 00:19:57,875
<i>Ini pasti berhantu.</i>

416
00:19:58,750 --> 00:20:00,292
<i>Pasti ada hantu gentayangan</i>

417
00:20:00,417 --> 00:20:02,542
<i>atau aku cuma teler berat.</i>

418
00:20:02,667 --> 00:20:04,292
<i>Panggil Zak Bagans.</i>

419
00:20:05,625 --> 00:20:07,250
<i>Putrimu setuju mau berbicara.</i>

420
00:20:10,708 --> 00:20:11,875
BRITT RAVEN
PANGGILAN MASUK

421
00:20:14,375 --> 00:20:15,708
Hei, Nak.

422
00:20:17,625 --> 00:20:18,875
<i>Ibu tewas.</i>

423
00:20:19,833 --> 00:20:21,208
Ayah tahu.

424
00:20:21,333 --> 00:20:23,167
<i>Astaga, ada banyak darah dan…</i>

425
00:20:23,292 --> 00:20:25,792
<i>Aku berusaha. Aku tahu tak boleh cabut pisaunya</i>

426
00:20:25,917 --> 00:20:27,000
<i>- karena kata Ayah…</i>
- Hei.

427
00:20:27,125 --> 00:20:29,375
<i>- …tapi dia mati, Ayah.</i>
- Perbuatanmu benar.

428
00:20:29,500 --> 00:20:31,042
<i>- Dia mati.</i>
- Dengar, kau…

429
00:20:31,167 --> 00:20:33,333
Perbuatanmu benar. Ibu tahu itu.

430
00:20:33,458 --> 00:20:35,625
- Ibumu tahu.
<i>- Tapi itu tak berhasil!</i>

431
00:20:38,333 --> 00:20:39,875
<i>Kenapa Ayah di sana?</i>

432
00:20:40,000 --> 00:20:42,125
<i>Kenapa mereka menuduh Ayah? Ayah di kantor, 'kan?</i>

433
00:20:42,250 --> 00:20:44,833
<i>- Kenapa mereka pikir Ayah pelakunya?</i>
- Mereka salah.

434
00:20:44,958 --> 00:20:46,708
Cuma itu. Ini semua salah.

435
00:20:46,833 --> 00:20:49,542
Cuma salah paham.

436
00:20:49,667 --> 00:20:52,000
<i>Kata Kakek, sidang Mercy cuma untuk yang bersalah.</i>

437
00:20:52,125 --> 00:20:54,250
Jangan dengarkan kakekmu, mengerti?

438
00:20:54,375 --> 00:20:56,625
Ayah tahu cara kerjanya, bisa ada kesalahan.

439
00:20:57,333 --> 00:20:58,833
Ini salah paham. Mengerti?

440
00:20:58,958 --> 00:21:00,667
<i>- Maka pulanglah.</i>
- Ini salah paham.

441
00:21:01,167 --> 00:21:03,625
<i>Kumohon, pulang saja.</i>

442
00:21:03,750 --> 00:21:05,750
Ayah pulang setelah ini beres.

443
00:21:05,875 --> 00:21:07,208
<i>Britt, kau yakin mau bicara?</i>

444
00:21:07,333 --> 00:21:09,458
<i>- Ada alasan ayahmu di sana.
- Pulanglah.</i>

445
00:21:09,583 --> 00:21:10,625
<i>- Biarkan dia, Chris.</i>
- Ya, Britt.

446
00:21:10,750 --> 00:21:12,792
Jeff, bisa kau mundur sebentar?

447
00:21:12,917 --> 00:21:14,000
Britt, dengar.

448
00:21:14,125 --> 00:21:15,917
- Dengarkan Ayah.
<i>- Berikan ponselnya.</i>

449
00:21:16,042 --> 00:21:18,000
Apa pun yang terjadi hari ini,

450
00:21:18,125 --> 00:21:20,750
Ayah tak menyakiti ibumu, mengerti?

451
00:21:20,875 --> 00:21:21,917
- Tak mungkin.
<i>- Britt.</i>

452
00:21:22,042 --> 00:21:24,000
Berjanjilah kau akan ingat itu

453
00:21:24,125 --> 00:21:25,417
dan berjanjilah

454
00:21:25,542 --> 00:21:26,708
- apa pun yang terjadi…
<i>- Cukup.</i>

455
00:21:26,833 --> 00:21:28,792
Jeff. Britt. Hei, Britt!

456
00:21:29,708 --> 00:21:30,917
Astaga!

457
00:21:31,458 --> 00:21:32,500
Dia bajingan.

458
00:21:32,625 --> 00:21:34,292
<i>Itu dihitung sebagai panggilanmu.</i>

459
00:21:35,667 --> 00:21:38,292
- Kenapa dia bersama mereka?
<i>- Selama sidang,</i>

460
00:21:38,417 --> 00:21:41,000
<i>orang tua istrimu
adalah kerabat hidup terdekatnya.</i>

461
00:21:41,125 --> 00:21:43,125
Kau dengar ucapannya kepada putriku?

462
00:21:44,000 --> 00:21:46,000
Dia mau membuatnya membenciku.

463
00:21:46,958 --> 00:21:48,708
Aku tak pernah cukup baik untuk Nic.

464
00:21:48,833 --> 00:21:51,000
<i>Tn. Raven, ini tak membantu kasusmu.</i>

465
00:21:51,125 --> 00:21:54,167
<i>- Waktu terus berjalan.</i>
- Karena mereka cuma menyetujui Mercy

466
00:21:54,292 --> 00:21:57,167
jika terlihat seolah-olah orang punya peluang

467
00:21:57,292 --> 00:21:58,417
untuk membela diri!

468
00:22:01,083 --> 00:22:03,458
Kita tahu bahwa jam ini

469
00:22:03,583 --> 00:22:04,667
cuma omong kosong.

470
00:22:05,750 --> 00:22:08,833
Kau sudah memutuskan
nasib orang di ruang sidang ini

471
00:22:09,458 --> 00:22:11,458
sebelum mereka duduk di kursi ini.

472
00:22:14,667 --> 00:22:15,875
Tamatlah aku.

473
00:22:16,500 --> 00:22:18,417
<i>Marah tak akan membantumu.</i>

474
00:22:18,542 --> 00:22:20,500
Astaga. Istriku sudah mati

475
00:22:20,625 --> 00:22:22,500
dan putriku dengar aku pelakunya.

476
00:22:22,625 --> 00:22:24,958
Jadi, ya, aku butuh waktu sebentar. Mengerti?

477
00:22:25,083 --> 00:22:26,875
Kau mengerti? Paham?

478
00:22:27,000 --> 00:22:29,042
<i>Aku tak dirancang untuk merasakan.</i>

479
00:22:29,167 --> 00:22:31,167
<i>Tugasku adalah memeriksa fakta.</i>

480
00:22:31,292 --> 00:22:33,250
<i>Jadi, aku tak mengerti,</i>

481
00:22:33,375 --> 00:22:35,000
<i>tapi aku memahami.</i>

482
00:22:35,125 --> 00:22:36,833
Kau memahami. Itu…

483
00:22:39,167 --> 00:22:41,958
Itu bagus. Baik, kau memahami.

484
00:22:43,208 --> 00:22:44,792
Sikap penangananmu luar biasa.

485
00:22:44,917 --> 00:22:47,250
<i>Aku juga memahami kau teralihkan oleh perasaanmu</i>

486
00:22:47,375 --> 00:22:48,833
<i>dan punya satu jam delapan menit</i>

487
00:22:48,958 --> 00:22:51,125
<i>untuk mengurangi kemungkinan bersalahmu</i>

488
00:22:51,250 --> 00:22:53,250
<i>sebanyak 5,5%.</i>

489
00:22:53,375 --> 00:22:56,167
<i>Jika kau tak bersalah, buktikan kepadaku.</i>

490
00:22:57,250 --> 00:22:59,792
<i>Jika tidak, Britt akan kehilangan
kedua orang tuanya.</i>

491
00:23:05,167 --> 00:23:06,167
Baik.

492
00:23:19,917 --> 00:23:21,000
<i>Tn. Raven.</i>

493
00:23:21,125 --> 00:23:22,125
Baik.

494
00:23:24,042 --> 00:23:25,208
Aku butuh rekanku.

495
00:23:26,333 --> 00:23:27,375
Panggil Jaq.

496
00:23:27,875 --> 00:23:31,000
{\an8}<i>Kau boleh menghubungi siapa saja selama sidangmu</i>

497
00:23:31,125 --> 00:23:33,333
{\an8}<i>untuk mengumpulkan bukti</i>

498
00:23:33,458 --> 00:23:35,750
{\an8}<i>atau meminta kesaksian karakter.</i>

499
00:23:35,875 --> 00:23:38,208
<i>- Yang mana?</i>
- Baik, aku mau rekanku.

500
00:23:38,333 --> 00:23:40,125
{\an8}<i>- Yang mana?</i>
- Yang kedua, karakter.

501
00:23:40,250 --> 00:23:41,417
{\an8}Jaq kenal aku dan Nic.

502
00:23:51,208 --> 00:23:52,667
<i>- Ya, halo.
- Detektif Diallo…</i>

503
00:23:52,792 --> 00:23:54,500
<i>ini dari ruang Sidang Mercy</i>

504
00:23:54,625 --> 00:23:57,583
<i>tempat Christopher Raven diadili
atas pembunuhan istrinya.</i>

505
00:23:57,708 --> 00:23:59,708
<i>Aku tahu. Aku sudah dengar.</i>

506
00:23:59,833 --> 00:24:02,708
<i>- Chris, kau kacau, Bung.</i>
- Jaq, tak mungkin ini ulahku.

507
00:24:02,833 --> 00:24:04,542
Kau harus percaya. Aku…

508
00:24:05,625 --> 00:24:07,958
{\an8}Tunggu. Siapa yang pertama di TKP?

509
00:24:08,083 --> 00:24:10,292
{\an8}<i>Unit udara. Hei, aku boleh masuk?</i>

510
00:24:10,417 --> 00:24:12,208
<i>Ya, masuklah.</i>

511
00:24:12,333 --> 00:24:13,833
<i>- Aku di dalam.</i>
- Bagus.

512
00:24:14,750 --> 00:24:15,958
Aku harus melihat TKP.

513
00:24:17,792 --> 00:24:18,792
Jaq, ayolah.

514
00:24:19,917 --> 00:24:21,167
<i>Hei, dengar, Chris.</i>

515
00:24:21,833 --> 00:24:23,417
- Jaq, tunjukkan…
<i>- Tn. Raven?</i>

516
00:24:23,542 --> 00:24:24,708
<i>Tunjukkan bukti atau…</i>

517
00:24:24,833 --> 00:24:27,125
Aku mencari bukti, akan kutunjukkan secepatnya.

518
00:24:27,250 --> 00:24:29,042
Aku butuh fail TKP.

519
00:24:29,167 --> 00:24:30,583
MENGAKSES // FAIL TKP

520
00:24:30,708 --> 00:24:31,500
KANTOR KORONER

521
00:24:34,250 --> 00:24:36,708
- Baik, Jaq, ayo berkeliling.
<i>- Hei, Chris…</i>

522
00:24:37,500 --> 00:24:39,417
<i>kita harus perjelas sesuatu dulu.</i>

523
00:24:39,542 --> 00:24:41,042
<i>Kau tahu aku mau bantu,</i>

524
00:24:41,167 --> 00:24:42,458
<i>tapi jika sepertinya buruk,</i>

525
00:24:42,583 --> 00:24:45,125
<i>aku akan mengatakannya kepadamu, mengerti?</i>

526
00:24:45,250 --> 00:24:47,750
<i>Setiap sidang Mercy harus mengirim pesan</i>

527
00:24:47,875 --> 00:24:50,833
<i>dan jika pesan hari ini
adalah polisi tak kebal hukum,</i>

528
00:24:51,542 --> 00:24:53,500
<i>aku tak akan suka, tapi aku bisa tidur.</i>

529
00:24:53,625 --> 00:24:56,042
<i>Tak ada yang lebih penting dari sidang itu.</i>

530
00:24:56,167 --> 00:24:59,083
- Itu adil.
<i>- Detektif Diallo, silakan.</i>

531
00:24:59,208 --> 00:25:00,583
<i>Baiklah.</i>

532
00:25:00,708 --> 00:25:02,000
<i>Mari berkeliling.</i>

533
00:25:02,125 --> 00:25:04,083
Boleh lihat pindaian TKP?

534
00:25:07,375 --> 00:25:08,417
Yang Mulia.

535
00:25:08,542 --> 00:25:09,750
<i>Silakan.</i>

536
00:25:09,875 --> 00:25:11,792
MENGAKSES // PINDAIAN TKP

537
00:25:13,792 --> 00:25:16,042
<i>Sekarang merender rekonstruksi imersif</i>

538
00:25:16,167 --> 00:25:18,208
<i>berdasarkan data yang ada.</i>

539
00:25:24,625 --> 00:25:26,875
Bisa perbesar itu? Resolusi penuh.

540
00:25:27,667 --> 00:25:29,083
<i>Vas pecah.</i>

541
00:25:29,667 --> 00:25:31,250
<i>Mungkin defensif.</i>

542
00:25:31,958 --> 00:25:33,292
<i>Menurutmu Nicole melawan?</i>

543
00:25:33,417 --> 00:25:36,250
<i>Ada di sini. Aku akan memutarnya.</i>

544
00:25:36,375 --> 00:25:38,083
<i>Periksa dua kali dengan log.</i>

545
00:25:38,208 --> 00:25:40,250
<i>Chris? Kau pikir Nicole melawan?</i>

546
00:25:40,375 --> 00:25:42,417
Ya. Mungkin.

547
00:25:43,333 --> 00:25:44,750
<i>Hei, bisa bereskan ini?</i>

548
00:25:44,875 --> 00:25:45,958
<i>Baik, Detektif.</i>

549
00:25:48,000 --> 00:25:49,250
Jaq, ke dapur.

550
00:25:53,250 --> 00:25:54,625
<i>Chris, kau tak mau lihat ini.</i>

551
00:25:54,750 --> 00:25:56,125
Jaq, tunjukkan kepadaku.

552
00:25:58,208 --> 00:26:00,958
<i>Kau boleh ke dapur, Detektif Diallo.</i>

553
00:26:15,625 --> 00:26:16,875
Jejak kaki siapa itu?

554
00:26:17,750 --> 00:26:19,333
<i>Jejak kaki putrimu.</i>

555
00:26:20,292 --> 00:26:21,667
Astaga.

556
00:26:21,792 --> 00:26:23,375
<i>Ada perlawanan.</i>

557
00:26:28,042 --> 00:26:29,583
Apa itu? Di atas meja.

558
00:26:31,458 --> 00:26:34,000
Di sana. Sudut jauh. Mendekat.

559
00:26:34,125 --> 00:26:37,583
<i>Memuat rekonstruksi TKP dari data trajektori.</i>

560
00:26:37,708 --> 00:26:39,000
Lihat itu?

561
00:26:39,125 --> 00:26:40,833
Pasti Nic melemparnya.

562
00:26:40,958 --> 00:26:44,708
- Artinya pelakunya di dapur.
<i>- Nic mundur.</i>

563
00:26:45,833 --> 00:26:47,167
<i>Mungkin sambil melempar piring.</i>

564
00:26:47,292 --> 00:26:49,417
Pelakunya maju. Jadi, sudah pegang pisau.

565
00:26:50,917 --> 00:26:52,417
<i>Pisaunya mudah diambil.</i>

566
00:26:53,750 --> 00:26:55,042
Baik, lihat sidik jarinya.

567
00:27:02,042 --> 00:27:03,833
PISAU DAPUR
BUKTI: SENJATA PEMBUNUHAN

568
00:27:03,958 --> 00:27:04,958
SIDIK JARI

569
00:27:07,583 --> 00:27:10,208
SIDIK JARI CHRIS RAVEN
SIDIK JARI: CHRIS RAVEN COCOK

570
00:27:10,333 --> 00:27:13,083
Nic takut pisau itu.
Aku yang selalu menyiapkan bahan.

571
00:27:15,083 --> 00:27:16,083
Ada serat?

572
00:27:21,000 --> 00:27:22,458
RAMBUT DI TAPLAK MEJA
SAMPEL: CHRIS RAVEN COCOK

573
00:27:22,583 --> 00:27:24,583
Semua seratnya cocok, Jaq.

574
00:27:24,708 --> 00:27:27,083
Rambutku, kulitku, ada DNA-ku di mana-mana.

575
00:27:30,542 --> 00:27:32,208
Kau memikirkannya. Katakan.

576
00:27:32,708 --> 00:27:35,458
<i>Ini kejahatan emosional biasa, Chris.</i>

577
00:27:35,583 --> 00:27:37,125
<i>Kekerasan impulsif,</i>

578
00:27:37,250 --> 00:27:38,792
<i>mengambil senjata terdekat,</i>

579
00:27:39,542 --> 00:27:40,542
<i>darahnya.</i>

580
00:27:42,000 --> 00:27:43,500
<i>Semuanya mengarah kepadamu.</i>

581
00:27:47,333 --> 00:27:48,792
<i>- Tn. Raven.</i>
- Dia benar.

582
00:27:48,917 --> 00:27:50,708
Ini kejahatan emosional tipikal.

583
00:27:52,750 --> 00:27:54,083
Jika benar, periksa seperti itu.

584
00:27:54,208 --> 00:27:55,708
Boleh lihat riwayat telepon Nic?

585
00:27:58,333 --> 00:28:01,292
<i>Ini salinan virtual interaktif ponsel Nicole.</i>

586
00:28:01,417 --> 00:28:02,958
<i>Kata sandinya sudah dilewati.</i>

587
00:28:04,458 --> 00:28:05,792
SISA WAKTU

588
00:28:07,000 --> 00:28:08,333
Baik, aku harus melihat…

589
00:28:08,458 --> 00:28:10,042
Boleh lihat riwayat telepon?

590
00:28:10,167 --> 00:28:11,833
Ya, nomor yang tak dia simpan.

591
00:28:11,958 --> 00:28:15,375
<i>Sebanyak 33% panggilan dan pesan
berasal dan mengarah ke ponselmu,</i>

592
00:28:15,500 --> 00:28:16,958
<i>26% dengan Britt,</i>

593
00:28:17,083 --> 00:28:18,542
<i>10% dengan orang tuanya,</i>

594
00:28:18,667 --> 00:28:20,167
<i>sisanya teman dan kolega</i>

595
00:28:20,292 --> 00:28:21,542
<i>- di Viking Shipping.</i>
- Tunggu.

596
00:28:21,667 --> 00:28:23,958
Malam saat kami bertengkar, dia mengirim pesan.

597
00:28:24,083 --> 00:28:25,667
Boleh lihat video Britt lagi?

598
00:28:29,083 --> 00:28:29,958
{\an8}IBU_AYAH_BERTENGKAR.mp4

599
00:28:30,083 --> 00:28:31,417
<i>Aku mengandalkan jabatan letnan</i>

600
00:28:31,542 --> 00:28:33,333
<i>- untuk itu.
- Britt butuh kamar sendiri.</i>

601
00:28:33,458 --> 00:28:34,750
<i>Kau sudah menjanjikannya.</i>

602
00:28:35,375 --> 00:28:37,083
<i>Itu basemen. Cuma perlu dinding gipsum.</i>

603
00:28:37,208 --> 00:28:39,292
<i>- Mundur dariku!
- Mundur?</i>

604
00:28:39,417 --> 00:28:40,875
<i>Tulis blog sesukamu.</i>

605
00:28:42,292 --> 00:28:43,792
<i>- Kau bicara dengan siapa?</i>
- Lihat?

606
00:28:43,917 --> 00:28:45,667
<i>- Tak ada.</i>
- Dia bicara dengan seseorang.

607
00:28:45,792 --> 00:28:46,750
<i>Dari kantor.</i>

608
00:28:46,875 --> 00:28:48,625
Temukan itu siapa. Di sana.

609
00:28:48,750 --> 00:28:50,042
<i>Aku sudah memindai ponselnya.</i>

610
00:28:50,167 --> 00:28:52,458
<i>Tak ada riwayat pesan pada waktu itu.</i>

611
00:28:52,583 --> 00:28:53,583
Kalau ponsel bekerjanya?

612
00:28:54,250 --> 00:28:56,083
<i>Aku tak punya riwayat ponsel kedua.</i>

613
00:28:56,208 --> 00:28:57,625
<i>Hei, ada ponsel lain di sini?</i>

614
00:28:57,750 --> 00:28:58,875
<i>Tidak. Tak ada.</i>

615
00:28:59,000 --> 00:29:01,000
Tentu saja. Mereka tak mencarinya.

616
00:29:01,125 --> 00:29:02,458
<i>Bisa coba telepon?</i>

617
00:29:02,583 --> 00:29:04,625
- Aku tak tahu nomornya.
<i>- Pernah kau telepon?</i>

618
00:29:06,708 --> 00:29:07,750
Apa? Kau tahu ponselku?

619
00:29:07,875 --> 00:29:10,875
<i>Ini terdaftar di awan munisipal
dan terbuka bagi sidang.</i>

620
00:29:11,667 --> 00:29:13,042
Viking memberikannya

621
00:29:13,167 --> 00:29:15,667
kurasa enam bulan lalu, mungkin waktu itu.

622
00:29:15,792 --> 00:29:17,042
Ya, itu.

623
00:29:17,167 --> 00:29:18,417
Aku di sidang remaja, dia mau aku

624
00:29:18,542 --> 00:29:19,917
melihat furnitur untuk basemen.

625
00:29:20,042 --> 00:29:21,292
MENGHUBUNGI…

626
00:29:22,292 --> 00:29:24,667
<i>Mungkin dalam mode senyap.</i>

627
00:29:26,042 --> 00:29:28,125
<i>Detektif, ada ponsel di sini.</i>

628
00:29:40,583 --> 00:29:42,083
<i>Detektif Diallo, bisa pastikan</i>

629
00:29:42,208 --> 00:29:44,417
<i>Bluetooth di ponselmu menyala?</i>

630
00:29:44,542 --> 00:29:46,167
<i>Dekatkan kedua ponsel.</i>

631
00:29:49,458 --> 00:29:50,875
