841
00:38:50,708 --> 00:38:52,750
<i>- Ini harus dihentikan.
- Kenapa merekamku?</i>

842
00:38:52,875 --> 00:38:55,625
<i>Jangan mendekat. Tak akan kuserahkan ponselnya.</i>

843
00:38:55,750 --> 00:38:57,083
<i>Tak akan kuserahkan. Kubilang,</i>

844
00:38:57,208 --> 00:38:59,583
<i>- "Jangan mendekat."
- Kenapa kau merekamku?</i>

845
00:38:59,708 --> 00:39:01,583
<i>- Aku merekammu karena…
- Kenapa?</i>

846
00:39:01,708 --> 00:39:05,292
<i>Aku merekammu karena aku mau kau melihatnya
saat kau tak mabuk. Paham?</i>

847
00:39:05,417 --> 00:39:08,208
Mereka sangat bangga kepadaku
saat aku berhenti mabuk.

848
00:39:08,333 --> 00:39:09,625
Nic, Britt, Rob.

849
00:39:09,750 --> 00:39:12,167
<i>Kutelepon AA.
Aku ikut pertemuan pertama hari Selasa.</i>

850
00:39:18,292 --> 00:39:19,333
<i>Aku merindukanmu.</i>

851
00:39:20,083 --> 00:39:21,125
<i>Aku rindu kalian.</i>

852
00:39:22,333 --> 00:39:23,792
<i>Setahun.</i>

853
00:39:23,917 --> 00:39:25,083
<i>Setahun.</i>

854
00:39:25,667 --> 00:39:27,167
<i>- Sehari.
- Setahun sehari.</i>

855
00:39:27,292 --> 00:39:28,375
<i>Aku dapat ini kemarin.</i>

856
00:39:28,958 --> 00:39:30,000
<i>Cepat sekali.</i>

857
00:39:30,125 --> 00:39:31,708
<i>Cepat sekali. Kau hebat.</i>

858
00:39:32,417 --> 00:39:33,750
<i>Terima kasih.</i>

859
00:39:33,875 --> 00:39:35,833
<i>- Sama-sama.
- Aku tak kuat empat kali,</i>

860
00:39:35,958 --> 00:39:37,542
<i>jadi mungkin aku minum lagi.</i>

861
00:39:38,083 --> 00:39:39,208
Aku tak tahan.

862
00:39:41,250 --> 00:39:42,792
Itu terus memengaruhiku.

863
00:39:42,917 --> 00:39:45,292
<i>Tn. Raven, apa yang kau bicarakan?</i>

864
00:39:45,417 --> 00:39:46,417
Ray.

865
00:39:46,958 --> 00:39:48,792
<i>Kematian rekan lamamu?</i>

866
00:39:52,250 --> 00:39:53,250
Bukan.

867
00:39:54,375 --> 00:39:55,833
Yang seharusnya kulakukan.

868
00:39:57,083 --> 00:40:00,417
<i>W-45, kami memeriksa SUV
yang dicurigai tabrak lari.</i>

869
00:40:01,542 --> 00:40:03,958
<i>Pelat nomor California, 3DHI832.</i>

870
00:40:04,083 --> 00:40:05,583
<i>PCH, di selatan Topanga.</i>

871
00:40:06,208 --> 00:40:08,542
<i>- Sepertinya dibuang dan kabur.
- Ya.</i>

872
00:40:08,667 --> 00:40:11,208
<i>- Kendaraan dipastikan dicari.
- Dimengerti.</i>

873
00:40:11,333 --> 00:40:12,333
<i>Baik, ayo periksa.</i>

874
00:40:13,500 --> 00:40:15,417
<i>Ya. Tak bisa bicara, Nic.</i>

875
00:40:15,542 --> 00:40:16,875
<i>Tidak.</i>

876
00:40:17,000 --> 00:40:18,333
<i>Bicaralah. Aku saja.</i>

877
00:40:20,667 --> 00:40:22,333
<i>Ya. Tidak, dia bisa.</i>

878
00:40:23,792 --> 00:40:24,958
<i>Tidak, Sayang.</i>

879
00:40:27,000 --> 00:40:29,250
<i>Tidak. Nic, hanya…</i>

880
00:40:29,375 --> 00:40:30,458
<i>Sayang, kau harus kurangi.</i>

881
00:40:30,583 --> 00:40:32,292
<i>Aku bisa apa? Mau aku ke kantor ketuaku</i>

882
00:40:32,417 --> 00:40:33,833
<i>dan bilang istriku punya petisi?</i>

883
00:40:33,958 --> 00:40:36,458
<i>Dia mau kita membuka kasus pasti yang lama?</i>

884
00:40:37,125 --> 00:40:39,333
<i>"Dia dapat banyak tanda tangan.
Dia minta baik-baik"?</i>

885
00:40:41,167 --> 00:40:42,625
<i>Tidak, hanya saja…</i>

886
00:40:44,500 --> 00:40:47,542
<i>Sayang, lebih buruk lagi ayahmu membela…</i>

887
00:40:47,667 --> 00:40:48,583
<i>Senjata!</i>

888
00:40:48,708 --> 00:40:49,792
<i>- Ada dua!
- Ray!</i>

889
00:40:49,917 --> 00:40:52,292
<i>- Ada dua. Chris!
- Ray!</i>

890
00:40:52,958 --> 00:40:55,917
<i>Kau yakin tak apa-apa?
IGD UCLA tak jauh dari sini.</i>

891
00:40:56,042 --> 00:40:57,083
<i>Tidak, ini tidak patah!</i>

892
00:40:57,208 --> 00:40:58,667
<i>Tetap kejar bedebah itu!</i>

893
00:40:58,792 --> 00:41:00,500
<i>Opsir Vale tertembak. Aku akan cegat.</i>

894
00:41:00,625 --> 00:41:01,792
<i>Aku butuh ambulans sekarang!</i>

895
00:41:01,917 --> 00:41:03,042
<i>Ambulans di jalan. Ganti.</i>

896
00:41:04,167 --> 00:41:05,958
<i>Hei. Bertahanlah, Ray.</i>

897
00:41:06,083 --> 00:41:07,542
<i>Hei, tetap bersamaku, Ray.</i>

898
00:41:07,667 --> 00:41:08,750
<i>Ray!</i>

899
00:41:19,667 --> 00:41:21,792
<i>Ray! Bicaralah, Ray!</i>

900
00:41:23,125 --> 00:41:25,375
<i>Opsir tumbang!</i>

901
00:41:25,958 --> 00:41:28,000
<i>Ini H13. Dimengerti.</i>

902
00:41:28,583 --> 00:41:29,958
<i>Hei, tiarap!</i>

903
00:41:30,083 --> 00:41:31,042
<i>Dia kabur.</i>

904
00:41:37,708 --> 00:41:39,083
<i>Polisi! Berhenti!</i>

905
00:41:39,208 --> 00:41:41,208
Seharusnya kutembak dia di sana.

906
00:41:41,333 --> 00:41:42,417
<i>Berhenti!</i>

907
00:41:44,792 --> 00:41:46,625
<i>Kemari! Berhenti!</i>

908
00:41:48,875 --> 00:41:50,458
<i>Berbalik. Tangan di kepala.</i>

909
00:41:50,583 --> 00:41:51,750
Seharusnya kubunuh dia.

910
00:41:54,083 --> 00:41:56,875
Setiap hari aku berharap aku membunuhnya.

911
00:41:58,792 --> 00:42:00,625
{\an8}<i>Putusan 4-B, kami para juri,</i>

912
00:42:00,750 --> 00:42:02,417
{\an8}<i>memutuskan Alex Varga</i>

913
00:42:02,542 --> 00:42:04,958
{\an8}<i>tidak bersalah atas pembunuhan Ray Vale.</i>

914
00:42:05,083 --> 00:42:07,042
{\an8}Kukira perbuatanku benar.

915
00:42:07,167 --> 00:42:08,500
{\an8}Menangkap penjahatnya,

916
00:42:08,625 --> 00:42:10,500
{\an8}biarkan pengadilan yang menghukumnya,

917
00:42:10,625 --> 00:42:11,625
{\an8}tapi dia tak dihukum.

918
00:42:14,417 --> 00:42:16,750
Kurasa mabuk-mabukan meredamnya.

919
00:42:16,875 --> 00:42:18,375
<i>Tn. Raven, kau tidak fokus.</i>

920
00:42:18,500 --> 00:42:20,042
<i>Bisa katakan apa yang kau ingat?</i>

921
00:42:22,750 --> 00:42:24,542
MEMBUKA // LINI MASA CHRIS RAVEN

922
00:42:29,208 --> 00:42:31,000
{\an8}Aku ke kantor pagi ini,

923
00:42:31,125 --> 00:42:32,417
meraih botolnya.

924
00:42:32,542 --> 00:42:33,583
Tak ada di sana.

925
00:42:33,708 --> 00:42:36,292
Aku tahu dia menemukannya, jadi aku pulang.

926
00:42:36,417 --> 00:42:37,625
<i>Lalu kau berdebat?</i>

927
00:42:37,750 --> 00:42:39,000
Tentu saja aku berdebat.

928
00:42:40,750 --> 00:42:42,625
Dia marah karena aku minum lagi.

929
00:42:42,750 --> 00:42:44,208
Aku marah kepadanya

930
00:42:44,333 --> 00:42:46,792
karena dia sudah membuang botolku
ke tempat sampah.

931
00:42:51,167 --> 00:42:53,500
<i>Jangan masuk! Keluar dari rumahku!</i>

932
00:42:53,625 --> 00:42:55,583
<i>Keluar dari rumahku! Jangan berani.</i>

933
00:42:55,708 --> 00:42:57,000
<i>Aku dilarang masuk ke rumahku?</i>

934
00:42:57,125 --> 00:42:58,167
<i>Ini bukan rumahmu!</i>

935
00:42:58,292 --> 00:43:00,833
<i>Katakan kau taruh di mana. Di mana botolku?</i>

936
00:43:04,708 --> 00:43:06,375
Jadi, kurusak vas favoritnya.

937
00:43:08,792 --> 00:43:10,167
Kulempar ke lantai

938
00:43:10,292 --> 00:43:11,792
karena aku tahu itu berharga baginya.

939
00:43:13,250 --> 00:43:14,917
Pecahannya mengenainya.

940
00:43:15,042 --> 00:43:17,708
Aku berusaha membantunya,
kurasa darahnya mengenaiku.

941
00:43:17,833 --> 00:43:19,792
<i>Kenapa kau tak mengakuinya tadi?</i>

942
00:43:19,917 --> 00:43:21,875
Ayolah. Itu tak terlihat bagus.

943
00:43:22,000 --> 00:43:25,292
Semuanya yang baru kukatakan
cuma membuat ini lebih buruk bagiku.

944
00:43:28,417 --> 00:43:29,833
Setelah itu,

945
00:43:29,958 --> 00:43:32,542
aku benar-benar tak ingat apa pun.

946
00:43:32,667 --> 00:43:34,667
Aku di rumah berdebat dengannya.

947
00:43:35,375 --> 00:43:36,750
Lalu saat sadar,

948
00:43:37,417 --> 00:43:39,875
aku menonton iklan di Sidang Mercy.

949
00:43:40,000 --> 00:43:41,000
<i>Ibu?</i>

950
00:43:42,292 --> 00:43:44,708
Kurasa jika dia marah
sampai memberitahuku soal Burke…

951
00:43:46,542 --> 00:43:47,583
Aku cuma bilang…

952
00:43:49,667 --> 00:43:52,208
- mungkin kau benar soal motif.
<i>- Tn. Raven.</i>

953
00:43:52,333 --> 00:43:55,333
Jika aku sudah marah,
mungkin aku mengambil pisaunya…

954
00:43:55,458 --> 00:43:56,792
<i>Jika kau mengaku bersalah,</i>

955
00:43:56,917 --> 00:43:59,250
<i>sidang ini mewajibkanku memutuskan,</i>

956
00:43:59,375 --> 00:44:02,125
<i>lalu kau tinggal menunggu waktunya habis.</i>

957
00:44:02,250 --> 00:44:04,625
Sudah 98%. Maddox, ayolah.

958
00:44:04,750 --> 00:44:07,417
<i>Jika ingatanmu tentang kejadian di rumah</i>

959
00:44:07,542 --> 00:44:09,250
<i>dengan Nicole benar-benar hilang,</i>

960
00:44:10,208 --> 00:44:12,375
<i>maka kau tidak mampu mengaku bersalah.</i>

961
00:44:13,208 --> 00:44:14,458
<i>Namun, persentase bersalahmu</i>

962
00:44:14,583 --> 00:44:17,875
<i>tetap lebih dari cukup untuk mengeksekusimu,</i>

963
00:44:18,000 --> 00:44:22,167
<i>tapi kau tetap mendapat bantuanku sepenuhnya.</i>

964
00:44:22,292 --> 00:44:23,917
<i>Jadi, jika kau akan mati hari ini,</i>

965
00:44:24,917 --> 00:44:27,000
<i>apa kau tak mau mencoba mengungkapkan</i>

966
00:44:27,125 --> 00:44:29,458
<i>kebenarannya dengan pasti sebelum itu?</i>

967
00:44:31,333 --> 00:44:33,292
<i>Meski kebenarannya kelam.</i>

968
00:44:35,208 --> 00:44:36,375
Justru itu.

969
00:44:39,875 --> 00:44:41,542
Mungkin aku tak mau tahu pasti.

970
00:44:42,542 --> 00:44:44,042
Dari sudut pandangku sekarang,

971
00:44:44,792 --> 00:44:48,667
yang membuatku berpikir mungkin aku
tak membunuh Nic adalah bertanya-tanya,

972
00:44:48,792 --> 00:44:53,458
bagaimana aku melakukan kejahatan emosional
jika tak ada emosi lagi?

973
00:44:58,000 --> 00:45:01,292
KANTOR KORONER
AUTOPSI OLEH: DR. FIONA COX

974
00:45:07,750 --> 00:45:09,125
Sial.

975
00:45:09,250 --> 00:45:13,083
Menurutmu kira-kira itu?

976
00:45:13,208 --> 00:45:14,458
<i>Aku tak paham maksudmu.</i>

977
00:45:14,583 --> 00:45:16,417
Maddox, aku berpikir sendiri.

978
00:45:16,542 --> 00:45:18,208
<i>Berpikir itu senyap karena otak…</i>

979
00:45:18,333 --> 00:45:20,417
Itu cuma ungkapan, Yang Mulia.

980
00:45:22,167 --> 00:45:23,167
Jadi, boleh kuteruskan?

981
00:45:23,292 --> 00:45:25,083
Aku boleh terus mencari bukti?

982
00:45:25,208 --> 00:45:27,333
<i>Selama kau tak mengaku membunuhnya,</i>

983
00:45:27,458 --> 00:45:29,417
<i>ya, kau boleh gunakan sisa waktumu.</i>

984
00:45:31,292 --> 00:45:32,292
Siapa?

985
00:45:32,792 --> 00:45:33,792
Kenapa?

986
00:45:35,000 --> 00:45:36,333
Bagaimana?

987
00:45:36,458 --> 00:45:38,333
<i>- Tn. Raven?</i>
- Masih berpikir.

988
00:45:40,208 --> 00:45:42,417
Tunjukkan orang yang rutin kontak dengan Nic.

989
00:45:42,542 --> 00:45:44,500
<i>Protokol sidang ini mewajibkanku</i>

990
00:45:44,625 --> 00:45:47,292
<i>menekankan bahwa melakukan investigasi pembunuhan</i>

991
00:45:47,958 --> 00:45:49,667
<i>cuma dalam waktu 40 menit…</i>

992
00:45:49,792 --> 00:45:50,500
Bagus. Wah.

993
00:45:50,625 --> 00:45:52,042
<i>…peluang suksesnya kecil.</i>

994
00:45:52,167 --> 00:45:53,292
Kau mau aku duduk diam

995
00:45:53,417 --> 00:45:55,500
dan menunggu mati? Kau mencegahku mengaku!

996
00:45:55,625 --> 00:45:57,750
<i>Sidang ini cuma memastikan kau sadar…</i>

997
00:45:57,875 --> 00:45:59,125
- Aku hampir tertipu.
<i>- …bahwa kau…</i>

998
00:45:59,250 --> 00:46:03,000
Aku sempat berpikir mungkin tempat ini
bukan tempat eksekusi.

999
00:46:05,542 --> 00:46:08,500
<i>Ini semua individu
yang rutin berhubungan dengan istrimu.</i>

1000
00:46:11,500 --> 00:46:12,583
Terima kasih, Yang Mulia.

1001
00:46:16,875 --> 00:46:19,667
{\an8}Dalam pembunuhan berencana,
biasanya korbannya kenal dekat.

1002
00:46:21,417 --> 00:46:23,208
{\an8}Kita bisa kecualikan Burke.

1003
00:46:24,083 --> 00:46:25,083
{\an8}Orang tuanya juga.

1004
00:46:27,875 --> 00:46:29,667
Bisa pisahkan teman dan pekerjaan?

1005
00:46:32,250 --> 00:46:34,542
KOLEGA NICOLE - 16
TEMAN NICOLE - 9

1006
00:46:37,000 --> 00:46:38,333
Ada 25 orang.

1007
00:46:38,458 --> 00:46:39,542
Tambahkan ke papan.

1008
00:46:43,583 --> 00:46:44,708
Ayolah, Nic, siapa?

1009
00:46:48,208 --> 00:46:50,208
Kurasa dia benar.

1010
00:46:50,333 --> 00:46:51,667
{\an8}<i>- Siapa?</i>
- Burke.

1011
00:46:52,208 --> 00:46:54,917
{\an8}Jika aku ada untuknya,
mungkin dia akan bercerita…

1012
00:46:55,042 --> 00:46:56,542
{\an8}<i>Orang yang mendengarkannya, tentang putrimu…</i>

1013
00:46:56,667 --> 00:46:58,708
<i>- Cukup.
- …dan masalah pekerjaannya.</i>

1014
00:46:58,833 --> 00:47:00,417
<i>Kau cuma perlu sedikit lebih memperhatikan…</i>

1015
00:47:00,542 --> 00:47:03,042
Burke! Aku butuh Burke. Sekarang.

1016
00:47:04,000 --> 00:47:07,542
<i>Tn. Burke sedang diproses di Jalan 77.</i>

1017
00:47:07,667 --> 00:47:09,208
KANTOR POLISI JALAN 77

1018
00:47:09,333 --> 00:47:11,583
<i>- Memproses.</i>
- Ya, siapa opsir prosesmu?

1019
00:47:11,708 --> 00:47:14,500
<i>- Aku. Siapa ini?</i>
- Chris Raven, Kejahatan Berat.

1020
00:47:14,625 --> 00:47:15,958
Aku butuh Patrick Burke.

1021
00:47:16,083 --> 00:47:17,083
<i>Sedang daftar sidik jari.</i>

1022
00:47:17,875 --> 00:47:19,792
<i>Tunggu, katamu Raven?</i>

1023
00:47:19,917 --> 00:47:22,375
<i>- Bukankah kau orang yang…</i>
- Ya, orang itu.

1024
00:47:22,500 --> 00:47:24,333
<i>Kurasa aku tak perlu memberinya…</i>

1025
00:47:24,458 --> 00:47:26,917
<i>Opsir, ini Hakim Maddox dari Sidang Mercy.</i>

1026
00:47:27,042 --> 00:47:29,333
<i>Tolong berikan Tn. Burke ponselmu.</i>

1027
00:47:29,458 --> 00:47:31,667
<i>Aku akan segera ke Burke.</i>

1028
00:47:31,792 --> 00:47:32,875
<i>Terima kasih.</i>

1029
00:47:33,000 --> 00:47:34,458
Baik. Mau hubungi OPK-ku nanti?

1030
00:47:34,583 --> 00:47:36,167
<i>Organisasi Pemeliharaan Kesehatan</i>

1031
00:47:36,292 --> 00:47:39,333
<i>terkenal dengan prosedur rumitnya
dan proses lambatnya.</i>

1032
00:47:41,750 --> 00:47:42,833
<i>Jadi, kau bercanda.</i>

1033
00:47:43,500 --> 00:47:45,833
Lihat, kau juga berpikir.

1034
00:47:47,083 --> 00:47:48,083
<i>Hei, Burke!</i>

1035
00:47:48,708 --> 00:47:50,750
<i>- Ya?
- Ada telepon.</i>

1036
00:47:51,542 --> 00:47:52,542
<i>Siapa?</i>

1037
00:47:56,083 --> 00:47:57,167
<i>- Raven?</i>
- Bicara kepadaku

1038
00:47:57,292 --> 00:47:58,417
atau ke hakim.

1039
00:47:59,125 --> 00:48:00,625
Katamu Nic butuh pendengar.

1040
00:48:00,750 --> 00:48:01,917
Apa masalahnya?

1041
00:48:02,042 --> 00:48:03,375
Ada masalah dengan teman?

1042
00:48:03,500 --> 00:48:04,792
<i>Tidak.</i>

1043
00:48:04,917 --> 00:48:05,917
<i>Kau tahu, hal biasa.</i>

1044
00:48:06,042 --> 00:48:08,667
<i>Yang punya bayi berpikir dia pusat dunia.</i>

1045
00:48:08,792 --> 00:48:10,417
<i>Yang satu lagi tak adil saat bayar.</i>

1046
00:48:10,542 --> 00:48:11,542
Kalau soal pekerjaan?

1047
00:48:12,125 --> 00:48:13,125
<i>Wah.</i>

1048
00:48:13,667 --> 00:48:15,792
<i>Kau benar-benar tak tahu apa pun.</i>

1049
00:48:17,792 --> 00:48:20,125
<i>Baik, kubilang kepadanya itu sepele,</i>

1050
00:48:20,250 --> 00:48:21,792
<i>tapi dia sangat stres karena itu.</i>

1051
00:48:21,917 --> 00:48:23,792
<i>Dia tak suka mengintai.</i>

1052
00:48:23,917 --> 00:48:25,667
