1763
01:19:32,333 --> 01:19:33,833
Kau tahu itu salah.

1764
01:19:34,792 --> 01:19:36,333
<i>Havelock, lakukan sekarang.</i>

1765
01:19:36,458 --> 01:19:37,917
Tidak!

1766
01:19:38,042 --> 01:19:39,333
Havelock, dengarkan aku!

1767
01:19:39,458 --> 01:19:41,167
Ada hakim terpintar di dunia di sini.

1768
01:19:41,292 --> 01:19:43,375
- Biar dia memutuskan.
<i>- Jika dia cukup cepat,</i>

1769
01:19:43,500 --> 01:19:46,292
<i>semua orang di gedung ini dan truk itu akan mati.</i>

1770
01:19:46,417 --> 01:19:48,250
Kumohon, Maddox.

1771
01:19:48,375 --> 01:19:49,375
<i>Tidak.</i>

1772
01:19:50,083 --> 01:19:51,292
Jangan Britt.

1773
01:19:51,417 --> 01:19:53,500
<i>Chris, sebaiknya aku tak ikut campur.</i>

1774
01:19:53,625 --> 01:19:55,167
