1775
01:20:01,417 --> 01:20:02,792
Jangan!

1776
01:20:07,292 --> 01:20:09,208
<i>- Sial!
- Gagal. Tak terpicu!</i>

1777
01:20:09,333 --> 01:20:10,542
<i>Tak terpicu! Awas!</i>

1778
01:20:10,667 --> 01:20:13,625
<i>Tak terpicu! Menyingkir! Masuk!</i>

1779
01:20:21,792 --> 01:20:23,083
Itu perbuatanmu?

1780
01:20:23,792 --> 01:20:25,417
<i>Kita kehabisan pilihan.</i>

1781
01:20:25,542 --> 01:20:27,583
<i>Chris, kau dengar?</i>

1782
01:20:31,542 --> 01:20:33,333
<i>Dia berbelok ke arah Mercy.</i>

1783
01:20:35,750 --> 01:20:36,875
<i>Jaraknya tiga menit.</i>

1784
01:20:37,000 --> 01:20:38,958
<i>Aku akan mengumumkan evakuasi.</i>

1785
01:20:39,083 --> 01:20:40,875
<i>Harap segera evakuasi.</i>

1786
01:20:42,458 --> 01:20:44,375
<i>Harap segera evakuasi.</i>

1787
01:20:44,500 --> 01:20:45,958
<i>Semua tim, masuk.</i>

1788
01:20:46,083 --> 01:20:47,625
<i>Harap segera evakuasi.</i>

1789
01:20:48,333 --> 01:20:49,750
<i>Harap segera evakuasi.</i>

1790
01:20:49,875 --> 01:20:51,500
Jaq, aku butuh kau.

1791
01:20:51,625 --> 01:20:53,250
<i>- Untuk apa?</i>
- Coba bicara dengannya.

1792
01:20:53,375 --> 01:20:54,583
Maddox, kau setuju?

1793
01:20:54,708 --> 01:20:57,625
<i>Detektif Diallo, taruh unit udaramu
di depan truknya.</i>

1794
01:20:57,750 --> 01:21:00,042
<i>Kau harus merekam wajah pengemudinya.</i>

1795
01:21:00,167 --> 01:21:01,875
<i>Sedekat mungkin.</i>

1796
01:21:02,000 --> 01:21:03,000
<i>Dimengerti.</i>

1797
01:21:08,500 --> 01:21:11,542
<i>Sekarang kau terhubung dengan saluran radionya.</i>

1798
01:21:11,667 --> 01:21:13,000
Rob? Kau dengar aku?

1799
01:21:13,125 --> 01:21:14,667
<i>- Hei, astaga.</i>
- Ini Chris.

1800
01:21:14,792 --> 01:21:16,792
<i>Kau tak bisa membujukku, Chris.</i>

1801
01:21:16,917 --> 01:21:17,958
<i>- Ayah, tolong!</i>
- Rob,

1802
01:21:18,083 --> 01:21:19,750
kau bisa hentikan ini. Lepaskan Britt.

1803
01:21:19,875 --> 01:21:21,500
<i>Saat kau masuk ke pertemuan AA,</i>

1804
01:21:21,625 --> 01:21:24,708
<i>aku tahu siapa dirimu sebenarnya.</i>

1805
01:21:24,833 --> 01:21:26,958
<i>Kau menggentayangi mimpiku, Chris.</i>

1806
01:21:27,083 --> 01:21:28,917
<i>Saudaraku punya masalah,</i>

1807
01:21:29,042 --> 01:21:30,250
<i>tapi aku bisa membantunya.</i>

1808
01:21:30,375 --> 01:21:31,750
<i>Aku bisa memperbaikinya.</i>

1809
01:21:31,875 --> 01:21:33,208
<i>Kau yang memulai semua ini.</i>

1810
01:21:33,333 --> 01:21:35,542
Jika ini salahku dan hakim ini, kenapa kau…

1811
01:21:35,667 --> 01:21:37,083
<i>Aku perlu kau di kursi itu.</i>

1812
01:21:37,208 --> 01:21:39,958
<i>Kau harus menderita di kursi itu,
mengetahui kau tak bersalah.</i>

1813
01:21:40,083 --> 01:21:42,208
