1818
01:21:49,292 --> 01:21:51,625
<i>Tidak. Aku sudah berusaha. Aku menelepon.</i>

1819
01:21:51,750 --> 01:21:53,667
<i>Kita tak boleh membiarkannya!</i>

1820
01:21:53,792 --> 01:21:55,542
<i>Katanya jika aku…</i>

1821
01:21:55,667 --> 01:21:56,792
