1823
01:21:58,792 --> 01:21:59,833
<i>Ini omong kosong!</i>

1824
01:21:59,958 --> 01:22:01,583
<i>Menurutmu apa? Aku bisa menembaknya.</i>

1825
01:22:01,708 --> 01:22:03,083
