<i>- Berhenti!</i>

1826
01:22:03,208 --> 01:22:04,208
MENGAKTIFKAN // KONTROL QUADCOPTER

1827
01:22:10,042 --> 01:22:11,083
Astaga.

1828
01:22:11,208 --> 01:22:12,375
SISA WAKTU

1829
01:22:25,833 --> 01:22:29,042
<i>- Daya mati. Baterai cadangan diaktifkan.</i>
- Maddox!

1830
01:22:29,167 --> 01:22:30,500
