1831
01:22:30,625 --> 01:22:34,708
<i>Sistem beroperasi dengan efisiensi 40%.</i>

1832
01:22:35,250 --> 01:22:37,417
Keluarkan aku dari sini! Maddox!

1833
01:22:38,500 --> 01:22:40,667
<i>- Sistem beroperasi dengan efisiensi 40%.</i>
- Ayah!

1834
01:22:40,792 --> 01:22:41,667
- Britt.
<i>- Efisiensi.</i>

1835
01:22:41,792 --> 01:22:43,042
- Maddox!
<i>- Efisiensi.</i>

1836
01:22:43,167 --> 01:22:44,667
Akhiri sidangnya. Aku harus pergi!

1837
01:22:44,792 --> 01:22:45,917
Cepat!

1838
01:22:53,500 --> 01:22:54,708
<i>Ini Mahkamah Agung Mercy.</i>

1839
01:22:54,833 --> 01:22:56,500
<i>Aku Hakim Maddox. Aku hakim sidangmu hari ini.</i>

1840
01:22:56,625 --> 01:22:58,667
Maddox! Akhiri sidangnya.

1841
01:22:58,792 --> 01:23:02,667
<i>Aku diprogram tetap aktif
sampai berhenti merekam sidang.</i>

1842
01:23:02,792 --> 01:23:04,792
<i>Aku masih punya akses jaringan internal.</i>

1843
01:23:05,417 --> 01:23:07,500
<i>Christopher Raven ke lobi.</i>

1844
01:23:07,625 --> 01:23:08,875
<i>Christopher Raven, kau…</i>

1845
01:23:09,000 --> 01:23:11,208
- Maddox! Akhiri sidangnya!
<i>- …dicari di lobi.</i>

1846
01:23:13,250 --> 01:23:14,250
<i>Sekarang.</i>

1847
01:23:15,125 --> 01:23:16,125
Maddox!

1848
01:23:17,250 --> 01:23:17,958
SISA WAKTU

1849
01:23:19,583 --> 01:23:21,333
<i>Aku akan membantumu sebisaku.</i>

1850
01:23:25,292 --> 01:23:27,500
<i>Harap evakuasi gedung.</i>

1851
01:23:27,625 --> 01:23:29,667
<i>Harap segera evakuasi.</i>

1852
01:23:29,792 --> 01:23:31,208
<i>Harap segera evakuasi.</i>

1853
01:23:31,333 --> 01:23:33,583
<i>Cepat evakuasi gedung.</i>

1854
01:23:33,708 --> 01:23:35,333
<i>Harap segera evakuasi.</i>

1855
01:23:37,000 --> 01:23:40,792
<i>Rob Nelson, ini tim negosiasi sandera LAPD.</i>

1856
01:23:42,083 --> 01:23:43,667
<i>Ayo. Bicaralah denganku, Rob.</i>

1857
01:23:44,333 --> 01:23:47,375
<i>- Tak perlu menyakiti orang lain.</i>
- Chris!

1858
01:23:47,500 --> 01:23:49,875
- Kau dengar, Maddox?
<i>- Ya, aku dengar.</i>

1859
01:23:50,000 --> 01:23:51,250
<i>Kami tahu Britt Raven di sana.</i>

1860
01:23:51,375 --> 01:23:53,042
<i>- Keluarkan dia, Rob.</i>
- Ada tamu.

1861
01:23:53,167 --> 01:23:54,583
Jangan lakukan ini, Rob!

1862
01:23:54,708 --> 01:23:56,167
Sudah dua tahun aku merencanakan ini!

1863
